{"tid":1930228,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一齊去投訴邱騰華喇","createTime":"2020-03-17T11:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T16:21:57.000Z","uid":170988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c07133e5b07ebc78cfe58e86a8a81309af67d2a7","tid":1930228,"uid":170988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今日表示，香港電台作為公共廣播機構，港台雖然擁有編輯自主，惟須接受一定制約，包括要遵守《香港電台約章》，並且聽取港台顧問委員會的意見，如不聽取需要解釋。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華並且說，港台同樣受通訊事務管理局的制約，任何市民可就節目提出意見及投訴，通訊局有責任及法定權力處理，多少人對個別節目的欣賞，對投訴結果起不到作用，「如果有人提出某些節目有好多的欣賞數字，這恐怕不能作為處理投訴的一種對沖。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A8%B1%E9%A0%88%E7%A7%89%E5%85%AC%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%B0%8D-%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF-%E6%AC%A3%E8%B3%9E%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96/#.XnC1FQS9VTk.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25A0%2588%25E7%25A7%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E8%25B3%259E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B2%2596%2F%23.XnC1FQS9VTk.facebook&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBw0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=f8b4b954\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25A0%2588%25E7%25A7%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E8%25B3%259E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B2%2596%2F%23.XnC1FQS9VTk.facebook&h=ca52dc9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla